                    "value": "<p>The powder beetle attempts an @Check[athletics|against:fortitude] check against an adjacent creature's Fortitude DC. On a success, the beetle pushes the target 5 feet away (10 feet on a critical success). In low gravity, the target moves double the distance away and is pushed half the distance moved into the air during the movement (falling deals damage as normal).</p>"
